Morir So√±ando

Ingredients:
- 1   can of evaporated milk
- 1   Tbs of vanilla extract
- 1/4 cup of sugar
- 1   cup of ice
- 2   cups of orange juice (preferably freshly squeezed and strained)

Prep:
1. Put evaporated milk in fridge for at least 15 minutes or until its cold to the touch

Mix:
1. Add vanilla extract to evaporated milk and stir
2. Add sugar to orange juice until is a bit too sweet and stir til sugar is completely dissolved 
3. Add ice to orange juice and stir till very cold 
4. Mix orange juice and evaporated milk and stir
5. Enjoy!
